posts.content: 🍺 Fresh this week
Hazy & Freshy with AIBA Gold
Availability: On tap, growler fills & tinnies

This super sessionable Aussie lager is crisp, clean and ultra refreshing. Brewed with a light malt base, perfectly balanced by subtle passionfruit and citrus notes. Don’t think too hard, just enjoy.

ABV 4.2%
Availability: On tap, growler fills & tinnies
Dry & Refreshing Sour Ale

This ridiculously refreshing beer (formerly known as Sourpuss) is our take on the classic Berliner Weisse style. Bursting with bright raspberry flavours, balanced by zippy tartness and a crisp, dry finish. It’s Summer in a glass (or straight from the can).

ABV 3.8%
We drop new releases every month, each featuring different styles of beer and showcasing our favourite hops.
